text: Ðis is seo boc þæ Æðelstan cing gæbocode Ælfheagæ bisceope to þam bisceop stolæ on Winceastre of Ticceburnan.
Of ellen forda on cealc swyðe dell.
Of cealc swyðe delle on melan beorh.
Of mælan beorge on hig leage.
Of þam ægscce to steortan leage.
Eall swa þæt heah hylte scæt to scagan.
Of scagan eall swa þio wrid wale scæt of hit cymð to woh hlincan on þæne ymb stocc.
Of ðam ymb stocce on wiðig mære.
Of wiðig mære on þæne æscstubb.
Of earnes beorge on syfan wyllan.
Of syfan wyllan on hafeces del.
Of aþulfes heale to langan leage.
Of langan leage to mænan leage.
Of wines heafdan on ellen ford.
